{ lib, buildRosPackage, fetchurl, ament-cmake, ament-cmake-cppcheck, ament-lint-common, builtin-interfaces, geographic-msgs, geometry-msgs, rosidl-default-generators, rosidl-default-runtime, std-msgs }:
